        <title>Workstation KDE error</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[0brand]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <code>Namis</code></p>
<p>This could be a RAM issue.  Use <code>rads</code> to lower your RAM in your VMs and see if that helps. Keep RAM over 512 MB for desktop environment. Also shutdown all not vital processes on your host to free up RAM.</p>
